Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.83,0:01:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第二十六唱 天空和未來之頌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.94,0:02:08.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.36,0:02:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難以置信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.04,0:02:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蕾居然被同契
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.56,0:02:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是看那表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.19,0:02:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是平常的那個她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.92,0:02:22.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們絕對無法對蕾芙麗·梅札蘭斯大人下手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.13,0:02:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這次一定要了結一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.25,0:02:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼如此卑鄙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.58,0:02:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隨你怎麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.01,0:02:42.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.49,0:02:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.18,0:02:44.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明白了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.11,0:02:46.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷 龍威 奇雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.22,0:02:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在只有封住蕾的武器了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.82,0:02:51.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不傷害蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.51,0:02:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只毀掉武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.83,0:02:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,解除同契
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.46,0:03:16.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.25,0:03:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這孩子真厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.97,0:03:28.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和擬煌珠相比簡直有如天壤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.60,0:03:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.67,0:03:31.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,力量像是源源不斷地涌出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.06,0:03:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還是不要再做垂死掙扎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.33,0:03:37.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,七煌寶樹在我們手中的現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.04,0:03:39.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們已沒有贏的可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.48,0:03:48.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一口氣幹掉他們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.38,0:03:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,會被你們幹掉嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.54,0:03:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蕾說過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.24,0:03:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「和我在一起」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.22,0:03:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.65,0:04:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,會甘心被你們幹掉嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.48,0:04:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.84,0:04:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.64,0:04:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抵抗是沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.91,0:04:33.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.07,0:04:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.63,0:04:49.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.13,0:04:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們煌珠將終止你們守護者所締造的愚蠢的歷史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.11,0:05:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為了創造一個不再紛爭的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.54,0:05:02.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說是不再紛爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.08,0:05:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但不會打算和我們守護者共存的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.05,0:05:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 你們只要不反抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.30,0:05:13.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還是可以確保讓你們作為我們的道具生存的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.91,0:05:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不想爭戰的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.74,0:05:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,除此之外別無他法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.16,0:05:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,據古籍記載
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.95,0:05:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在久遠的太古時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.71,0:05:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個煌珠樂園尚在大地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.50,0:05:28.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,煌珠與守護者共存著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.80,0:05:31.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那裏每個人都哼著歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.58,0:05:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以語言的靈力引導各種事情向好的方面發展
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.58,0:05:39.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.94,0:05:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能行嗎 吉露露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.15,0:05:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.07,0:05:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜託了 莉莉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.44,0:05:47.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.37,0:05:51.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知何時守護者們忘記歌頌而相互紛爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.28,0:05:55.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,開始把煌珠作為戰鬥的道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.41,0:05:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.47,0:05:58.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因此充斥著世界的波動開始紊亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.00,0:06:00.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,煌珠樂園脫離開大地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.20,0:06:02.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,浮上了天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.64,0:06:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被守護者奪走了七煌寶樹的我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.87,0:06:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尊奉同伴中實力最強者為女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.85,0:06:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以其力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.81,0:06:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,延續至今
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.11,0:06:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.31,0:06:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那也就到今天為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.18,0:06:21.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,事到如今沒辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.42,0:06:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.68,0:06:24.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還是得把蕾...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.64,0:06:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把蕾封印起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.70,0:06:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.10,0:06:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,除此之外還有什麼辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.19,0:06:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,奇雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.63,0:06:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.48,0:06:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,波濤洶涌為之徵兆{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.26,0:06:42.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,澄淨心靈靜聽{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.04,0:06:45.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,祈求海神之救贖{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.06,0:06:47.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,朝向大海之原{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.89,0:06:49.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,敞開雙手{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.57,0:06:52.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鎮天之捧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.87,0:06:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.17,0:07:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.71,0:07:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.59,0:07:09.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.87,0:07:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們的這一行為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.16,0:07:23.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,正是不同種族無法共存的證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.38,0:07:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.13,0:07:29.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以你們所愛之人的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.46,0:07:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,送你們下地獄吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.20,0:07:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.86,0:07:51.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蕾也拚命地在抗爭著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.16,0:07:59.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.17,0:08:01.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請不要反抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.04,0:08:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蕾芙麗·梅札蘭斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.76,0:08:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和守護者交往的話又會有紛爭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.96,0:08:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,驅逐守護者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.93,0:08:12.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,創造煌珠的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.42,0:08:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那真的就是幸福嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.96,0:08:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,至少我不那麼認為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.90,0:08:18.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和守護者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.21,0:08:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和人類相遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.71,0:08:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,同契之後感覺到幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.29,0:08:25.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣的煌珠也是有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.35,0:08:30.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是被守護者豢養的煌珠的幻想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.79,0:08:31.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是幻想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.57,0:08:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,守護者 煌珠想法一致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.59,0:08:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定能相互理解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.63,0:08:42.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那為什麼會有守護翼的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.54,0:08:46.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們想要保護我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.70,0:08:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是我們根本就不想被保護
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.34,0:08:52.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然而
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.59,0:08:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們以「保護」這一迷人的名義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.33,0:08:57.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,巧妙地隔離我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.47,0:09:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這終究是因為視我們為危險的道具的緣故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.61,0:09:03.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想法一致？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.50,0:09:04.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是在撒謊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.93,0:09:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,的確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.41,0:09:08.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,的確或許是存在著錯誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.96,0:09:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是那...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.29,0:09:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是「也許有」就能解決的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.17,0:09:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但因此劫持守護者 改造成擬煌珠就是對的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.64,0:09:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們只不過是用同樣的手法報復而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.45,0:09:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以別再幹這種事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.03,0:09:27.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一再重演爭戰的不是你們嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.25,0:09:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,守護者中並不都是那樣的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.77,0:09:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,至少我們想和你們一起...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.60,0:09:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不管遭受多少教訓都不會平息干戈的守護者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.32,0:09:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,毫無未來可言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.42,0:09:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.26,0:09:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都住手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.24,0:09:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都住手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.40,0:09:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家如何如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.99,0:09:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,煌珠如何如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.66,0:10:00.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那些借口算什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.16,0:10:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我喜歡蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.73,0:10:12.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是因為蕾是煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.45,0:10:15.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是因為蕾是蕾才喜歡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.19,0:10:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以想一直在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.89,0:10:21.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.52,0:10:24.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就這樣不行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.04,0:10:36.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遺失頌詞的守護者沒有活著的價值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.69,0:10:37.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.56,0:10:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷 躲開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.09,0:10:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天地{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.99,0:10:52.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.07,0:10:57.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是你心中的所想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.05,0:11:00.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,將它原原本本地傳達出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.95,0:11:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要緊
