Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.85,0:13:42.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.29,0:13:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們的契約失效了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.17,0:13:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就是說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.24,0:13:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.24,0:13:50.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,做到了嗎 酷德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.25,0:13:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.01,0:14:00.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遺失的古代的頌詞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.90,0:14:04.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,居然 居然在這時出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.63,0:14:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我 錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.86,0:14:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜託
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.21,0:14:16.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要討厭守護者 人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.18,0:14:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.35,0:14:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家或許也會改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.81,0:14:25.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蕾芙麗·梅札蘭斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.29,0:14:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,歐琺斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.80,0:14:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是我們輸了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.31,0:14:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.17,0:14:34.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是奇怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.58,0:14:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有失敗感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.56,0:14:41.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.35,0:14:43.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.87,0:14:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,聽了酷的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.31,0:14:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,非常高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.97,0:14:50.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 嗯...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.34,0:14:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也要說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.04,0:14:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也想永遠和你在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.32,0:14:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.17,0:15:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷是酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.36,0:15:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.04,0:15:21.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了 他們兩個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.28,0:15:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.14,0:15:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.01,0:15:31.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,兩個人在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.90,0:15:34.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就是珍貴無比的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.19,0:15:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而我卻將它斬斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.77,0:15:41.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以她...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.44,0:15:45.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.52,0:15:47.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了 希絲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.19,0:16:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.78,0:16:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,各自又回到了自己的生活中努力了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.50,0:16:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,理想的狀況不知道能持續到什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.62,0:16:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但理想就是為了推動現實向理想靠近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.11,0:16:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,得努力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.58,0:16:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也為了已犧牲的無數的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.13,0:16:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不想再次重複悲傷的歷史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.86,0:17:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在守護翼總部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.55,0:17:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,正締結必不再戰的協議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.68,0:17:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,願今天的誓言在百年兩百年之後仍銘刻在心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.33,0:17:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也許理想實現是得在那麼久遠以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.72,0:17:19.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,敬請期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.33,0:17:24.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和平的日子的的確確來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.19,0:17:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對此我毫不懷疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.13,0:17:31.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對了 大家的近況也說一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.04,0:17:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拉撒蒂因為不用再戰鬥了鬆了一大口氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.48,0:17:41.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是聽說最近被莉莉雅逼著穿女裝很是頭疼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.05,0:17:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.55,0:17:51.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別看 別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.99,0:17:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這種衣服一點也不適合我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.04,0:17:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很配啊 姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.77,0:17:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.12,0:18:03.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,臥魯克斯好像就職於守護翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.17,0:18:06.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,上了 吉露露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.26,0:18:07.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.77,0:18:11.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然後...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.06,0:18:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,發現目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.68,0:18:21.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,航向東北1時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.86,0:18:23.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,偏轉45度方位
