Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.74,0:18:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.61,0:18:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.71,0:18:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,害怕嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.80,0:18:41.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.00,0:18:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.91,0:18:48.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抓緊哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.55,0:18:49.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.87,0:18:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一口氣衝過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.05,0:18:59.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.59,0:19:02.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗨 好久不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.07,0:19:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為 為什麼你會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.80,0:19:09.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想多增長些見識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.23,0:19:12.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這也是為了守護翼的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.57,0:19:13.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比起這些理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.20,0:19:15.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其實是想再次踏上旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.96,0:19:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊 是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.21,0:19:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和你們一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.60,0:19:20.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 好狡猾啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.41,0:19:21.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好地方就你們兩個人去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.51,0:19:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別礙手礙腳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.61,0:19:26.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是我和蕾的第一次出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.16,0:19:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在這種值得紀念的時刻相遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.88,0:19:33.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們果然是有緣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.55,0:19:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.89,0:19:36.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.52,0:19:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.99,0:19:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,感覺好高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.14,0:19:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.68,0:19:43.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.74,0:19:44.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.86,0:19:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家一起突擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.91,0:19:48.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.14,0:19:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,煌珠們已經保護起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.50,0:19:52.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,工作結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.07,0:19:55.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.84,0:20:04.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,少年和少女的冒險暫且告一段落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.19,0:20:08.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但同時兩人的故事又揭開了新的一頁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.65,0:20:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前方有什麼在等待著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.99,0:20:14.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也有困惑的時候吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.82,0:20:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也有流淚的日子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.27,0:20:17.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即便如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.26,0:20:21.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,相信兩人憧憬的未來是光明的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.20,0:20:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為那也是我們的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.84,0:20:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一直飛到那顆星那裏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.98,0:20:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.77,0:20:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能呼吸嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.73,0:20:56.35,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あの時君が見てた夢を追いかけて{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.73,0:20:56.35,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,追尋著你那時所見的夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.84,0:21:09.82,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,僕等は今遠い道を步き始めてる{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.84,0:21:09.82,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們此刻開始遠行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.88,0:21:24.38,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,君の目に映ってる世界の姿を{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.88,0:21:24.38,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,映現在你眼中的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.20,0:21:32.12,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,無口な指で分け合いたくて{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.20,0:21:32.12,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以無言的手指與你分擔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.19,0:21:39.11,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一人にはしないから{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.19,0:21:39.11,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不會讓你獨自一人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.31,0:21:51.84,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,君の為に少しでも優しくなれたかな{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.31,0:21:51.84,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為你盡量地溫柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.88,0:22:04.11,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,涙を微笑みに変える強さを僕は{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.88,0:22:04.11,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把眼淚化作微笑的堅強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.75,0:22:09.65,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,まだ知らない{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.75,0:22:09.65,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我還未知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.70,0:22:21.88,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,何よりかけがえのない君への想いが{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.70,0:22:21.88,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,無可替代的思念你之情意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.00,0:22:28.93,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,繰り返してた時の流れを{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.00,0:22:28.93,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把輪迴的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.30,0:22:36.77,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,未来へと変えて行く{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.30,0:22:36.77,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,流轉向未來

